Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:33.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:53.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:00.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:04.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.17,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:15.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:28.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:33.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:43.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人被導航電腦系統
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入為阿斯拉達GSX的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專屬駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此管生車隊的原駕駛員日吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法操縱 離隊而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由這位十四歲的少年隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來駕駛阿斯拉達GSX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加富士崗的地區預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對於只有電單車賽車經驗的隼人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛這種連成人賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有辦法隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控的「CYBER F0RMULA CAR」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛一個行進的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫向的G不過是瞬間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是機器  啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三話  燃燒吧 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:03:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分48秒235  好快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比場地記錄要慢個1.5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次試車成績算不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的維修站在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太過份了 讓小鬼開車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小孩開車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他們大概全都瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人怎麼回事 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子 沒受到什麼傷害真是幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去幫他拿點喝的過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在換輪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查懸吊繫統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做對時間上並沒有什麼幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車被一個初學者弄得烏煙瘴氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是太對不起這部車了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別囉嗦了 快動手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼跑完全程的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我繞了幾圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繞了幾圈都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像已經十幾圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠平安的回來還真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間 花了多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能平安的開回來那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔說得一點也沒錯 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止 大家收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該不會是不及格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然 為什麼不告訴我時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分l4秒223
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加的35輛車子裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名最後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子的行進記錄已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的駕駛感也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不愧是風見的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看錯你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督 檢查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我開一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間測驗不是有三次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有兩次的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車子可是你父親的精心傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你又是我好友的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們其中的任何一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要不撞車的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 人工智能系統的汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以保護駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…以監督的身份來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能再准你開的 聽到了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我有點失神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次我想再認真地駕駛一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟你父親真是一樣的固執
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你絕對不可以出事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子我們隊上也只有這部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管其他車子還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜地聽從電腦的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸設計的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種事情 不做做看怎麼會知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的時間是第四名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是「F-3」冠軍的新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再稍微用點心 第一名 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是破場地記錄也不是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一秒鐘的時間雖然不算短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟新條直輝非常地配合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個第一名是非我們莫屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 世界錦標賽也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開太慢了 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是告訴過你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是機器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠像電單車一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有風的感覺就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進入測時區了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次的時間出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點擔心隔壁那新車的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先偵察它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真多心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又看不到輪胎 都快窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是電單車的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的彎轉不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉彎的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不要太過傾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣非常容易發生事故的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是騎電單車的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓我仔細的瞧一瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的重力加速度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再降一檔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管它是不是新車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能夠好好駕駛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓你看看我的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻覺直路到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把翼壓低 降低空氣阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 我們可別輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進入600尺的轉彎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持風門全開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開雙翼 快要撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 加速過彎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 隼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 我沒什麼事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但車子已經撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子沒有全毀 是運氣好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你就不要再逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為經理代理人的我決定停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的事故到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做任何的辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看我下次的時間好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧隔壁那個小鬼 他好像已經不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子還要捲土重來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是隼人的行進路線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些檢查等一下再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的部份了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有奇怪的扭力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把聲音再重放一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速過彎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是騎電單車的一種技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運用加速度的力量以便車身轉向…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開的是四輪汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看看這一次競賽的輪跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很完整 可是他有利用這種技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說隼人他做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是在下意識的狀態下做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然車子本身有幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是反射神經相當好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當時的臨機應變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免了一場可怕的災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們意思怎麼樣 說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓他試試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他別那麼衝動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 隼人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何他都想做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不太贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這責任我來負好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到結果是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是孤注一擲於
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車之血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們原諒我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保持鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」已經過了測時線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀別太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個G能不能想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽聽引擎的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表示引擎也很吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 騎電單車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎的聲音宛如優美的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓引擎過於吃力這點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該跟電單車一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種像唱歌一樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要追上那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑我的技術不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別喪氣 鎮定點 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要冷靜才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 我可跟你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線路徑的時間是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分9秒604
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下該可以拿到好成績了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不愧是新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們再來一次加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸抓到訣竅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是到目前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的時間記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少管閒事 阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意 路面不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣闖過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像有風的感覺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我轉不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達快想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請明確的指示好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是電單車的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用氣式剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 轉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算過了那個彎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 終於跑完全程了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是使用氣式剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使後擾流板已經損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 謝謝你 阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是盡了該盡的義務罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是你不可愛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士崗選拔賽的最後結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績是1分47秒099的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵車隊的新條直輝選手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項成績雖然沒有打破場地的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對於初次參賽的新條直輝來講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是非常好的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在35輛車中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前24名已經通過了預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將可以參加決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下就是24名選手的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果出場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會那麼慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過手上長個水泡而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是想再通過預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經把後擾流板給弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跑完全程已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是第25名 很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽委員會通知剛才的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21名車號23號的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為違反「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般安全規定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第63條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,予以取消賽車資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此排名向上擠一名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第25名車號30號的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管生隊的隼人選手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦通過預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你通過預賽了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過預賽?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯不錯 通過預賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 好耶 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝先生你有什麼感想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於「CYBER F0RMULA」你有什麼感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 發表一下感想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝先生請等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

